Package: anrepr
Type: Package
Title: Analysis Reporting in R as a Hierarchical Graphical Logging
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Andrey","Tovchigrechko",email="andreyto@gmail.com",role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: A hierarchical graphical logging facility for saving dynamic and static plots, 
    tables and other analysis outputs from arbitrary locations inside your 
    analysis code and generating as your final output a static Web site with
    multiple pages containing auto-numbered and linked sections, plots and tables.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
